SYNQDRIVE PHASE 4 API STRUCTURE

Goal:
Design REST API structure.

Principles:
- multi tenant aware
- platform vs organization scope
- backend controls external integrations

------------------------------------------------
ROUTE GROUPS
------------------------------------------------

Platform routes:

/admin/organizations
/admin/users
/admin/products
/admin/prospects
/admin/integrations
/admin/billing
/admin/settings
/admin/dimo

------------------------------------------------
ORGANIZATION ROUTES
------------------------------------------------

/organizations/:orgId/stations
/organizations/:orgId/users
/organizations/:orgId/vehicles
/organizations/:orgId/customers
/organizations/:orgId/bookings
/organizations/:orgId/integrations

------------------------------------------------
VEHICLE ROUTES
------------------------------------------------

/vehicles
/vehicles/:vehicleId
/vehicles/:vehicleId/battery
/vehicles/:vehicleId/tires
/vehicles/:vehicleId/brakes
/vehicles/:vehicleId/service-events
/vehicles/:vehicleId/enrichment-jobs

------------------------------------------------
DIMO MIRROR ROUTES
------------------------------------------------

/admin/dimo/vehicles
/admin/dimo/non-registered
/admin/dimo/sync

------------------------------------------------
VEHICLE REGISTRATION FLOW
------------------------------------------------

1 fetch mirrored vehicle
2 prefill DIMO fields
3 add SynqDrive fields
4 create registered vehicle

------------------------------------------------
INTEGRATION ROUTES
------------------------------------------------

/integrations
/organizations/:orgId/integrations
/organizations/:orgId/integrations/connect
/organizations/:orgId/integrations/disconnect
/organizations/:orgId/integrations/logs

------------------------------------------------
BILLING ROUTES
------------------------------------------------

/billing/subscriptions
/billing/invoices
/billing/payments

------------------------------------------------
PROSPECT ROUTES
------------------------------------------------

/prospects
/prospects/import
/prospects/:id
/prospects/:id/activity
/prospects/:id/contacts

------------------------------------------------
RENTAL ROUTES
------------------------------------------------

/customers
/bookings
/bookings/:id